        <item>
            <title>中国机械人参展商用真女人扮女机械人 　「女仿生机械人」遭入场人士乱摸</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/28/robot-5/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=robot-5</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/28/robot-5/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 12:00:55 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[2024 世界机械人大会]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[仿真机械人]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[机械人]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1259074</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>中国近日于北京举行 2024 世界机械人大会，多个参展商展出其自家研发机械人，其中包括 27 款人形机械人。不过有民众发现，供入场人士触摸的女机械人竟然是由真人扮。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-8.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1259086" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-8-350x580.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-8-350x580.jpg 350w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-8.jpg 543w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 350px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-9.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1259087" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-9-350x580.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-9-350x580.jpg 350w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-9.jpg 543w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 350px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-2.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1259080" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-2-395x580.jpg" alt="" width="395" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-2-395x580.jpg 395w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-2.jpg 613w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 395px" /></a></p><p>根据入场人士拍摄的影片可见，「女机械人」引来大批入场人士围观，有不少人会触摸她们的身体、脸颊、头发，直呼与真人无异。由于她们所属的仿生机械人厂商未有表明「女机械人」是由真人扮演而成，不少人对她们上下其手乱摸，有人质疑厂商故意隐瞒事实欺骗大众，而在场人士亦借机故意「抽水」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1259082" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-4-395x580.jpg" alt="" width="395" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-4-395x580.jpg 395w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-4.jpg 613w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 395px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1259083" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-5-362x580.jpg" alt="" width="362" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-5-362x580.jpg 362w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-5.jpg 561w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 362px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1259084" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-6-350x580.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-6-350x580.jpg 350w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-6.jpg 543w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 350px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-7.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1259085" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-7-350x580.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-7-350x580.jpg 350w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-7.jpg 543w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 350px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1259081" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-3-395x580.jpg" alt="" width="395" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-3-395x580.jpg 395w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240828at-3.jpg 613w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 395px" /></a></p><p>此外，亦有影片亦拍到「女机械人」食饭及有职员帮手抺汗、吹风扇的画面。影片公开后随即引起网民热议，指「中国甚么都造假」、「中国人一天没造假才是国际大新闻」、「弄虚作假，中国就没有真正的机械人和 AI 还在那里骗人」、「大家都来摸，既然你中共想把别人当傻子，那大家就装疯卖傻」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uw1.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1259075" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uw1-473x580.png" alt="" width="473" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uw1-473x580.png 473w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uw1.png 735w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 473px" /></a></p><p>另有网民替「女机械人」抱打不平，「机械人小姐好委屈，本来是来 cos play 的，结果被妥妥的猥亵了，伦理道德真重要」、「有没有可能，猥琐男假装认不出真人，然后疯狂揩油机械人模特」、「那个假扮机械人的模特儿是不是哭了啊」、「观众质素也太低了」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uw12.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1259076" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uw12-487x580.png" alt="" width="487" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uw12-487x580.png 487w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uw12.png 755w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 487px" /></a></p><p>https://x.com/whyyoutouzhele/status/1828353547076796573</p><p>图片来源：影片截图</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.chinapress.com.my/20240828/%E6%AD%A3%E5%A6%B9%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E6%91%B8-%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E6%89%BE%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%AE%E7%9A%84/">中国报</a>、<a href="https://www.wenxuecity.com/news/2024/08/27/125746471.html">文学城</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/26/tesla-optimus-robot-in-element/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">香港抢先睇 Tesla Optimus 机械人　同场展出 Cybertruck、Model 3 + Model Y 新闪电银色</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/optimus-will-make-tesla-a-25-trillion-company/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Elon Musk 睇好 Optimus 机械人，预测 Tesla 市值提升至 25.5 万亿美元</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/28/robot-5/ai/">中国机械人参展商用真女人扮女机械人 　「女仿生机械人」遭入场人士乱摸</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
