        <item>
            <title>11 小时电池续航力   Sony WF-C510 入门级真无线耳机发表</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/28/sony-wf-c510-launched/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-wf-c510-launched</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/28/sony-wf-c510-launched/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 01:00:35 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony WF-C510]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1259003</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>昨日 Sony 发表全新入门级真无线耳机 WF-C510，外国媒体普遍认为它是 WF-C500 的升级版，但就以更亲民的价格带来全新设计和功能。首先，Sony WF-C510 的机身比上一代更加小巧，采用封闭式设计并搭配矽胶耳塞，提供 IPX4 等级防水能力，适合运动时佩戴。Sony 特别强调耳机外壳以回收塑料制造，符合环保理念。</p><p><span id="more-1259003"></span></p><p>虽然 Sony WF-C510 而入门级产品作为定位，但配备环境音模式，让用户能够听到周围环境的声音。不过 WF-C510 并未提供主动降噪，亦没有多点蓝牙连接功能。电池续航是 WF-C510 的卖点之一，官方公布单次充电可提供长达 11 小时的聆听时间，搭配充电盒使用更可达到 22 小时。耳机设有方便操作的实体按键，同时亦支援手机程式调整音效设定。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_13263"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/En7bLOQaDZM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>其他功能还包括 DSEE 数码音质增强引擎，以及 360 Reality Audio 环绕音效。比起上代 WF-C500 索价 100 美元，Sony 将全新的 WF-C510 定价为更具吸引力的 60 美元（约 468 港元）。耳机有黑、白、蓝和黄 4 种颜色选择，将会在 9 月初上市。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=1259015" rel="attachment wp-att-1259015"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1259015" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/08285a-694x463.jpg" alt="Sony WF-C510" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/08285a-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/08285a.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2024/08/27/sonys-budget-tws-earbuds-launch/">gizmochina</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/12/sony-zv-e10-ii-review/dc/dc-test/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Sony ZV-E10 II 拍片机影相一样得，毋须调色直出别具风格相片</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/sony-ult-wear-wh-ult900n/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Sony ULT WEAR WH-ULT900N 真无线重低音头戴耳机，两种重低音模式比较 + 性价比高 + 续航力高</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/28/sony-12/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PS5 日本加价 19%　Sony：受外部环境影响提高价格</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/28/sony-wf-c510-launched/mobile-music/headphones/">11 小时电池续航力   Sony WF-C510 入门级真无线耳机发表</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
